{
  "stem": "20684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we used to fight in the orphanages with knives because the boys in the orphanage had uniforms, gray uniforms, and we're different to all-- you know, Jewish all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And oddly enough, one of the famous kids in the orphanage-- not in ours, but in the one up the hill-- who were the [INAUDIBLE] boys, who came out of Buchenwald, was Elie Weasel was in the same group of orphanages I was.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he is most famous kids from the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Didn't do him much harm, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was there, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard about him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was a famous lawyer, international lawyer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But well, we got one Nobel prize winner out of-- out of the orphanages so it couldn't have been that bad.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We got a grand master in bridge, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He's talking to you at the moment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we'll come to that later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So things weren't all that bad in the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And yes, I used to come once a fortnight to Paris.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And my cousin used to take me to the pictures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was never allowed to handle the money because I was not to be trusted.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So my cousin used to buy me my ice cream and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And one day, I still remember today, which is another-- another bad day for me, that was already a year or two after I was in the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My uncle gave me 200 francs, which is equivalent to two-- two pictures' ticket, about $1 for-- on today's cost.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He gave me 200 francs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was after the war, 200 francs, not today's.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I was looking at it because I had never had any money of my own.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
